<p>During the migration, we ran into several bugs, performance issues, and =
missing features in Metro.
That isn't surprising for a framework in active development, especially whe=
n it is used in a
codebase of our size. We fixed some problems ourselves, but more often we r=
elied on Zac's guidance
and expertise to turn bug reports into production-ready fixes. Over the cou=
rse of the migration,
<a href=3D"https://github.com/search?q=3Drepo%3AZacSweers%2Fmetro%20is%3Apr=
